title: 05/25/21 DPS Best Of
itunes:title: 05/25/21 DPS Best Of
description:
On Today's Dan Patrick Show, DP reacts to Aaron Rodgers' conversation with Kenny Mayne last night as well as Julio Jones' phone call with Shannon Sharpe. What was Aaron's goal last night? Did Julio know he was live on air? The MMQB's Albert Breer shares what question he would have asked Aaron Rodgers. And Mike Florio of Pro Football Talk joins us to discuss how realistic a Julio Jones to the Packers trade would be.
